actions.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

official_title: A bill to extend the temporary suspension of duty on Styrene, ar-ethyl-,polymer with divinylbenzene and styrene beads having low ash content.

summary.text: Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend temporarily the suspension of duty on Styrene, ar-ethyl-,polymer with divinylbenzene and styrene beads having low ash content.

titles.title: A bill to extend the temporary suspension of duty on Styrene, ar-ethyl-,polymer with divinylbenzene and styrene beads having low ash content.
